                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900224-88-off478 t17900224-88-cd479"></join> last, putting him in fear, and feloniously taking from his person, and against his will, two pieces of callico, containing fifty-six yards, value 50 s. a piece of printed cotton, containing forty-nine yards, value 40 s. a linnen wrapper, value 9 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900224-88-victim848" type="victimName">
